---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base
  title="Notebook — Animations capturing ideas worth keeping · Clément Reiso"
  description="A personal collection of animations by Clément Reiso. Short videos that turn abstract ideas into something you can watch — built with Remotion."
>
  <section class="hero container">
    <p class="hero__eyebrow mono">A personal notebook</p>
    <h1 class="hero__title">
      Animations to remember<br />what I learn.
    </h1>
    <p class="hero__lede prose">
      This is a small corner of the internet where I keep the ideas I want to hold onto.
      Each one is turned into a short animation — a way to make abstract knowledge feel
      concrete, and to revisit it later without re-reading a book.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="intro container">
    <div class="prose">
      <h2>What you'll find here</h2>
      <p>
        Every page on this site is one animation. Press play, watch it through, and the
        idea will probably stick longer than a paragraph would. The collection grows
        slowly — quality over volume.
      </p>
      <p>
        Built with <a href="https://www.remotion.dev/">Remotion</a> for the videos and
        <a href="https://astro.build/">Astro</a> for the site itself. Both are open and
        the source lives on GitHub.
      </p>

      <h2>Currently</h2>
      <ul class="muted">
        <li>
          <a href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}circles-of-life/`}>Circles of life</a>
          — concentric rings of responsibility. Master the centre before you reach
          for the world.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>

<style>
  .hero {
    padding-block: var(--space-12) var(--space-8);
  }
  .hero__eyebrow {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
  }
  .hero__title {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
    max-width: 16ch;
  }
  .hero__lede {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: var(--leading-snug);
  }
  .intro {
    padding-block: var(--space-4) var(--space-8);
  }
  .intro h2 {
    margin-top: var(--space-6);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
  }
  .intro h2:first-child {
    margin-top: 0;
  }
</style>
